txt.en: You have defeated many Corsairs in the ruins of Ethillorn.
Although the damage they have dealt to Ethillorn will not be easily undone, you have weakened the Corsairs' forces in the ruins greatly and provided a respite for the people of Linhir and Lebennin.

Corsairs have taken Ethillorn and seek to use the port-town as a means to renew their attacks into Linhir and Lebennin. They must be defeated before they can mount a new assault against the people of Gondor.
Defeated Corsairs in the ruins of Ethillorn ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Corsairs of Umbar have seized the coastline of Lebennin and seek to pillage and destroy each coast-town until they reach Pelargir.
Defeat Corsairs in the ruins of Ethillorn ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

Corsairs can be found in the ruins of Ethillorn to the south of Linhir in Lower Lebennin.\n\nYou have encountered many Corsairs in the sacked town of Ethillorn and should work to weaken their hold so near to Linhir.
